==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Inclining
<hw>In*clin"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Inclination;
disposition.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>On the first <qex>inclining</qex> towards sleep.</q>
<rj><qau>Burke.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Party or side chosen; a following.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Both you of my <qex>inclining</qex>, and the rest.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Inclinnometer</ent>⟦br⟧
